\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Proof

\series bold
Inductive Step
\series default
: Let 
\begin_inset Formula $k\in\mathbb{Z}>5$
\end_inset

.
 Assume that 
\begin_inset Formula $P\left(k\right)$
\end_inset

 is true.
 Se we know that 
\begin_inset Formula $k!>k^{3}$
\end_inset

.
 We wish to prove 
\begin_inset Formula $P\left(k+1\right)$
\end_inset

, which states that 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left(k+1\right)!>\left(k+1\right)^{3}.
\]

\end_inset

To show this, we begin by manipulating the left hand side.
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\left(k+1\right)! & =\left(k+1\right)\left(k!\right)\quad\text{(By definition of factorail)}\\
 & >\left(k+1\right)k^{3}\quad\text{(Since we assume \ensuremath{P\left(k\right)})}\\
